WEBVTT

00:00:00.251 --> 00:00:05.075
This technological shift creates tension between business outcomes and human outcomes.

00:00:05.695 --> 00:00:12.601
Stagility is the balance between creating stability for workers while allowing the organization to move with extreme agility.

00:00:13.261 --> 00:00:15.703
Reflect on the practical payoff of this balance.

00:00:16.224 --> 00:00:22.028
Providing stable anchors like core values allows people to feel safe enough to innovate rapidly.

00:00:22.969 --> 00:00:28.533
Radical employee centricity involves partnering with employees to eliminate low-value work.

00:00:29.426 --> 00:00:30.792
This requires empathy.

00:00:31.454 --> 00:00:33.582
Cognitive empathy takes their perspective.

00:00:34.124 --> 00:00:40.770
Emotional empathy shares their feelings, and empathic concern senses what they need and takes decisive action.
